# Component Patterns & UI Guidelines

## UI Component Structure (components/ui/)

### Button Component
Located at [components/ui/Button.tsx](mdc:components/ui/Button.tsx)
```typescript
variants: "primary" | "secondary" | "outline" | "ghost"
sizes: "xs" | "sm" | "md" | "lg"
props: disabled, loading, className, onClick, type
```

### Input Component
Located at [components/ui/Input.tsx](mdc:components/ui/Input.tsx)
```typescript
props: label, placeholder, value, onChange, type, required, disabled, error, className
```

### Card Component
Located at [components/ui/Card.tsx](mdc:components/ui/Card.tsx)
```typescript
variants: "default" | "glass" | "modern"
padding: "none" | "sm" | "md" | "lg"
props: hover, className
```

